rComments: THE WORST TEACHER AT THIS SCHOOL. Consistently an A student, he marked my assignment and gave me a 49/100. Took it to the TA and I received an 81. That's a 32 mark difference. Skipped over things, paid no attention to points made. Highly arrogant. Avoid.

One of the worst profs I've had at UofT. Goes way too slow, lectures are hardly relevant to readings. Has difficulty in keeping the class engaged. When I look around the lecture hall, nearly a quarter of the students are sleeping and another quarter doing something else.

Waste of time. Watched more videos than he lectured. Didn't stay on schedule with the syllabus. Dragged points too long, neglecting covering others. The readings were all over the place. Rarely used the expensive text. Not engaging at all. Danced around topics instead of hitting us straight on. Very frustrating. The TAs sucked except for Matt.
